title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: A risk is only worth taking if you believe your odds are more than favorable today. A miscalculated attempt at a high-minded goal dashes your spirits if you fall short of expectations. You might reject someones criticism out of hand because you suspect your objectives are misunderstood. Although your suspicion may be correct, you need to work harder to clarify your intentions. Convert your anger into action by committing to improvement and accessibility. Bring your ideas down to earth and practice common sense. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
